snippet.title: Goodbye Dr. Sanchez Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
You and your friend have been kidnapped by the maniacal Dr. Carlos Sanchez. One of you managed to escape and now is wandering through the house. But the other remains imprisoned in a room with the necessary equipment to find the exit. The both of you must communicate to escape together!

Wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1456000/Goodbye_Dr_Sanchez/

Join our Discord server:
https://discord.gg/jc6EwWbKx7
